مثال: مشتق چند تابع محاسبه شده است:
الف) f(x) = -\frac{2}{3}x^4 \implies f'(x) = -\frac{8}{3}x^3
ب) g(x) = x^5 + 4x^3 - \sqrt{2}x + 1 \implies g'(x) = 5x^4 + 12x^2 - \sqrt{2}
پ) h(x) = (2x^2+1)(-x^2+7x-2) \implies h'(x) = 4x(-x^2+7x-2) + (2x^2+1)(-2x+7)
ت) t(x) = \frac{x^2-4}{3x+1} \implies t'(x) = \frac{2x(3x+1) - 3(x^2-4)}{(3x+1)^2}
